title: Artrosis - Discography
description:
Artrosis is a Polish gothic metal band founded in 1995 in Zielona Gora.

Current members
Magdalena Stupkiewicz-Dobosz \"Medeah\" - vocals 
Krystian Kozerawski \"MacKozer\" - guitar 
Remigiusz Mielczarek \"Remo\" - bass guitar 
Lukasz Migdalski \"Migdal\" - keyboards 
Konrad Biczak \"Lombardo\" - drums 

1997 - Ukryty Wymiar
1998 - W Imie Nocy
1999 - Hidden Dimension
1999 - Posrod Kwiatow I Cieni
2001 - Fetish
2001 - Fetish (english version)
2001 - In Nomine Notis
2002 - Melange
2006 - Con Trust
